text:
HubSpot automatically performs Brotli compression, prerendering, minification, image conversion to webp. <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/guides/speed#what-does-HubSpot-handle-for-you->

If Image sizes appear to the be the culprit in your speed tests then check out this section of that doc: <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/guides/speed#images>
